querysource.name: lista_articoli_in_collo
querysource.sql: select r.RPNMCOL as "collo", r.RPCDPRO as "codice", r.RPQTSPE as "quantita", c.PRDSTIT as "titolo", collo_cpnmcpe(r.ordprog,r.rpnmcol) as "qt_collo", collo_cppspre(r.ordprog,r.rpnmcol) as "peso_collo", collo_cptpfor(r.ordprog,r.rpnmcol) as "imballo_collo" from rig_prod r,catalogo c where r.ORDPROG=<? value('bolla') ?> and r.RPCDPRO=c.PRCDPRO order by collo, codice;

querysource.name: dati_ordine
querysource.sql: select ORDPROG as "ordprog", RONMCLL as "colli", RONMCPP as "copie", ordine_ropspre(ordprog) as "peso", data_ora(ROTMRCZ) as "data_lavorazione", RODSCLI1 as "desc_cliente", ROINCLI as "indirizzo_cliente", ROLOCLI as "localita_cliente", ROPRCLI as "provincia_cliente", ROCPCLI as "cap_cliente", data_ora('now') as "data_ora" from ric_ord where ORDPROG=<? value('bolla') ?>;
